                        As one of the high-tech enterprises, Beijing Tianshi Future Automation Engineering Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2000. The main business of our company is urban centralized heating industry.
                        We pay special attention to production automation and intend to manage information system for the construction and renovation of business as well.
                        We hold integrity-based business philosophy, making innovation as the priority and providing our customer with excellent service.
                        Our company is a comprehensive enterprise combining scientific research, production and engineering so as to create superior value for the centralized heating enterprises in innovation management, energy-saving and cost-reducing, low carbon and environmental protection.
                    </p>
                    <p class="p_row">
                        Beijing Tianshi Future Automation Engineering Technology Co., Ltd. has won a large group of outstanding scientific and engineering professionals who specialize in the field of automation of the heating industry with years of successful experience in service.
                        Our company developed and launched its own intellectual property rights of software and hardware products and has access to 5 utility model patents and 25 software copyright registrations.
                        Moreover, we have created xLink intelligent heating network monitoring and management System — a fusion of advanced technology and innovative applications. Our heat exchange station capacity is over 7,000 units. With its own talent, technology and product advantages, Beijing Tianshi Future Automation Engineering Technology Co., Ltd. has created the core competitiveness of enterprise.
                    </p> 
                    <p class="p_row">
                        Beijing Tianshi Future Automation Engineering Technology Co., Ltd. ,a enterprise that providing heating for provinces such as Beijing, Zhengzhou, Jinan, Shijiazhuang and large and medium enterprises in cities, has provided a total solution from the heat source, pipeline network to heat exchange station and to the user all-around automated monitoring and information management.
